io.github.struppigel.parser.sections.edata

Class ExportDirectory

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.struppigel.parser.sections.edata.ExportDirectory

  • public class ExportDirectory
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the directory table of the export section and provides access to the header values.

    The export directory table should be loaded by an ExportSection instance.
